videos.description: Tulsa's Dane Evans finds Josh Atkinson on a slant for a five-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Dane Evans gets Tulsa on the board with TD pass

videos.description: Central Michigan QB Cooper Rush makes an ill-advised pass that is intercepted by Tulsa's Jeremy Brady.
videos.headline: Tulsa makes big interception on ill-advised throw

videos.description: Kolton Shindelaris is called for targeting after a high hit on Central Michigan QB Cooper Rush and is ejected.
videos.headline: Tulsa's Kolton Shindelar ejected for targeting

videos.description: Tulsa CB Kerwin Thomas intercepts Central Michigan QB Cooper Rush's pass in the end zone.
videos.headline: Tulsa picks off Central Michigan in the end zone

videos.description: Tulsa's Dane Evans floats a pass to Keevan Lucas for his second touchdown pass of the game.
videos.headline: Evans extends Tulsa's lead with 2nd TD pass

videos.description: Tulsa QB Dane Evans finds TE Chris Minter all alone in the end zone for a four-yard score.
videos.headline: Dane Evans throws his 3rd TD of the first half for Tulsa

videos.description: Tulsa head coach Philip Montgomery talks about his team's up-tempo offense and defensive success in the 1st half
videos.headline: Tulsa head coach Philip Montgomery talks about his team's up-tempo offense and defensive success in the 1st half

videos.description: Central Michigan freshman kicker Kaden Keon boots a simple onside kick that the Chippewas are able to recover to start the second half.
videos.headline: Central Michigan recovers their own onside kick to start 2nd half

videos.description: On fourth-and-2, James Flanders barrels into the end zone from 17 yards out for a Tulsa touchdown.
videos.headline: Tulsa RB drags defenders into end zone for TD

videos.description: Dane Evans completes a 28-yard pass to Keevan Lucas for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Evans throws his fourth touchdown pass of the game, his second to Keevan Lucas

videos.description: Tulsa WR Keevan Lucas catches his third touchdown pass of the day from Dane Evans.
videos.headline: Keevan Lucas hauls in his third TD catch of the day for Tulsa

videos.description: Early in the fourth quarter, Central Michigan quarterback Cooper Rush gets his pass intercepted by Tulsa's Jesse Brubaker and returned 66 yards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Tulsa scores on pick-six to continue rout

videos.headline: J. Hayes run for 13 yds for a TD

videos.description: After Tulsa DT Jesse Brubaker intercepts a pass and takes it to the house, Brubaker walks up to WR Josh Atkinson on the sidelines, who is wearing a helmet and headbutts him without wearing one himself in celebration.
